25|$|When {{designing}} a facility, {{there are several}} things that {{should be kept in}} mind including <b>biosecurity,</b> worker safety and efficiency, and animal welfare. Diverse infrastructure is required in order to successfully collect and store genetic material. The buildings needed depend on the size of facilities as well as the extent of the operations.|$|E
